text: Luis Rodolfo Abinader Corona (born 12 July 1967) is a Dominican economist and politician. In 2020, he was elected President of the Dominican Republic. He was the Modern Revolutionary Party candidate for President of the Dominican Republic in the 2016, 2020 general elections, and 2024 general elections. ==Related pages== *List of scientists from North America ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Economists Category:Presidents of the Dominican Republic Category:Current national leaders
